title: Old Beef/Diss Track Storytime
description:
Tune in this week while Camo walks us down memory lane, sharing nitty gritty details about old conflicts they had back in their hometown which resulted in diss tracks, for all the tea listen up! 
For 50% off your first Care/of order, go to https://TakeCareOf.com and enter code “unfazed50”.
To match with a licensed therapist today, go to https://Talkspace.com and use code UNFAZED to get $100 off of your first month!
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
